CHANGES IN VERSION 1.3.1
------------------------

BUG FIX

	o translate(..., return.list=FALSE) throws error when the resulting list
	  is empty; corrected to return a matrix with no rows.

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.3
----------------------

SIGNIFICANT USER-VISIBLE CHANGES

    o Added function 'getOrthologs' and auxcillary functions 
	  that speeds up ortholog mappings in the Inparanoid databases.
	  
	o Added parameter 'simple' to 'translate' for improved 
      usage with lapply.	

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.0
----------------------

SIGNIFICANT USER-VISIBLE CHANGES

    o 'pickGO' can also filter on evidence.
	
	o Function for returning list and description of evidence 
	  for Gene Ontology ('getEvidenceCodes').
	  